# 🧠 Key Pattern in ACE Exam

Most questions ask:

> **Which GCP service best solves this problem?**

You should quickly map **problem → correct service**.

Example:

| Problem            | Service                      |
| ------------------ | ---------------------------- |
| Containers         | **Cloud Run**                |
| VM workloads       | **Compute Engine**           |
| Managed Kubernetes | **Google Kubernetes Engine** |
| Analytics          | **BigQuery**                 |
| Messaging          | **Pub/Sub**                  |
| Secrets            | **Secret Manager**           |

